product.name: Mobile Medical Privacy Screen Room Divider, 6 ft Tall Folding Portable Partition on Wheels for Office, Beauty Salon, Hospital, and Clinic (4)
product.description: Constructed with thickened iron pipes, this privacy screen is designed to resist deformation and cracking, Connected by durable hinges, the panels can be easily adjusted or folded to fit your needs. Equipped with solid, silent universal wheels and brake-equipped casters, the screen is easy to push and maneuver. Made from double-layer, fade-resistant, and washable nylon fabric, the screen is easy to clean and maintain, Perfect for various settings such as offices, beauty salons, hospital wards, clinics, massage rooms, and home bedrooms, providing privacy and functionality wherever needed.
product.bullet_points:
• Sturdy Iron Frame: Constructed with thickened iron pipes, this privacy screen is designed to resist deformation and cracking, providing excellent durability and a smooth, premium finish.
• Flexible Folding Design: Connected by durable hinges, the panels can be easily adjusted or folded to fit your needs. When not in use, the screen folds compactly for convenient storage, saving space.
• Smooth Mobility: Equipped with solid, silent universal wheels and brake-equipped casters, the screen is easy to push and maneuver, ensuring stable positioning and effortless movement.
• Hygienic Waterproof Fabric: Made from double-layer, fade-resistant, and washable nylon fabric, the screen is easy to clean and maintain, ensuring long-lasting hygiene and cleanliness.
• Versatile Applications: Perfect for various settings such as offices, beauty salons, hospital wards, clinics, massage rooms, and home bedrooms, providing privacy and functionality wherever needed.
